data.description: Move-in ready townhome located in the quiet community of Parkway Station. Conveniently located off of Highway 411 allowing for an easy commute to all of the restaurants, shopping, and entertainment that Cartersville has to offer. This property has a finished garage and a fenced-in patio that backs up to a tree line that will provide privacy and the perfect place to relax after a long day. Inside the classic vinyl plank floors throughout the property make cleaning a breeze. The open-concept living room leads to a dining and kitchen area, perfect for hosting and entertaining. All the stainless steel appliances, plenty of cabinet space, and granite countertops make the kitchen ideal for preparing meals. Each of the two spacious bedrooms provides ample storage with walk-in closets and ensuite bathrooms. This property is ready to become someone's next dream home.
